        <item>
            <title>HK Express 新 4 級行李制改逐件計　網民：加錢都解決不了問題</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/hk-express-2/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hk-express-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/hk-express-2/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:35:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅遊]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Hk Express]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1234304</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">國泰航空旗下的廉航香港快運（HK Express）宣佈修改政策，將推出四種票價，包括「輕便飛」、「隨心飛」、「經濟飛」、「無憂飛」，於今（8 日）起實行。宣佈新政策後，隨即引來網民不滿，指加錢都解決不了問題。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1234308 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsapp_2024050808_-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsapp_2024050808_-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsapp_2024050808_.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsapp_2024050808_-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲香港快運（HK Express）宣佈修改政策，將推出四種票價</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1234313 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441268715_9147867837-694x392.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441268715_9147867837-694x392.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441268715_9147867837.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1234315 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441191828_1328570501-670x580.jpg" alt="" width="670" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441191828_1328570501-670x580.jpg 670w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441191828_1328570501.jpg 1040w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 670px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1234316 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441897843_2108088746-666x580.jpg" alt="" width="666" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441897843_2108088746-666x580.jpg 666w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441897843_2108088746.jpg 1033w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 666px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲測試一下其他航空公司，試試來回大阪，選取相同日子，時間差不多，行李重量也差不多，比 HK Express 便宜 878 港元</p><p>以香港來回大阪為例，6 月 1 日至 6 月 7 日，現時在 HK Express 購買「無憂飛」，需要合共 3427 港元。而在其他航空公司同樣是香港來回大阪，選取相同日子，計算了所有費用，行李是 30KG，只需 2549 港元，足足比 HK Express 便宜 878 港元。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1234318 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240508_-1-1-563x580.jpg" alt="" width="563" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240508_-1-1-563x580.jpg 563w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240508_-1-1.jpg 874w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 563px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441187738_1203155681-646x580.png" alt="" width="646" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441187738_1203155681-646x580.png 646w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/441187738_1203155681.png 1002w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 646px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲宣佈新政策後，隨即引來網民不滿，指加錢都解決不了問題</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1234348 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240508_-1-2-694x119.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="119" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240508_-1-2-694x119.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240508_-1-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1234349 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240508_-1-3-694x136.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="136" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240508_-1-3-694x136.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240508_-1-3.jpg 848w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有網民在 HKExpress Facebook 貼文留言，指 HKExpress 將會失去原來優勢</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">HK Express 一宣佈新政策，網民隨即炮轟，只限隨身物品一件需要收取 388 港元，指如以往一樣登機就要收取 438 港元。有網民就批新政策不利攝影師，指自己每次都要帶相機、鏡頭及電腦，而物品不能寄倉，現時加錢都解決不了問題。亦有網民在 HKExpress Facebook 貼文留言，指 HKExpress 將會失去原來優勢，更指原本機票已不便宜，現時更多此一舉。</p><h2>行李 4 級制規定</h2><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 50%;"><h3>輕便飛</h3></td><td style="width: 50%;">可攜帶一件重量上限為 7kg 的隨身物品登機</p><p>不可攜帶行李喼</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">寄艙行李需另行預訂</p></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;"><h3>經濟飛</h3></td><td style="width: 50%;">可攜帶一件隨身物品及一件登機行李，重量上限一共為 7kg</p><p>寄艙行李需另行預訂</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;"><h3>隨心飛</h3></td><td style="width: 50%;">可攜帶一件重量上限為 7kg 的隨身物品登機</p><p>不可攜帶行李喼</p><p>1 件 20kg 寄艙行李</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 50%;"><h3>無憂飛</h3></td><td style="width: 50%;">可攜帶一件隨身物品及一件登機行李，重量上限一共為 7kg</p><p>包 1 件 32kg 寄艙行李</p><p>可選擇標準座位</td></tr></tbody></table><h2></h2><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.hkexpress.com/zh-hk/">HK Express</a>、<span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs xlh3980 xvmahel x1n0sxbx x1lliihq x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x4zkp8e x3x7a5m x1lkfr7t x1lbecb7 x1s688f xzsf02u x1yc453h" dir="auto"><a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 xggy1nq x1a2a7pz x1heor9g xt0b8zv x1hl2dhg x1s688f" role="link" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/638762621229829/">HK Express 香港快運及旅行資訊關注組</a></span>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/HKExpress/posts/pfbid02BpSHYujwN5ZoGxUmmeMT1S2Y99WeyhZLJJj19S5or4RZkwqx1cjxAqVia5Pg2uFNl">HK Express 香港快運 Facebook</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/hk-express-2/life-tech/travel/">HK Express 新 4 級行李制改逐件計　網民：加錢都解決不了問題</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
